title: Large Closets, Ample Parking, Full Size Washers & Dryers*
posting_body: ['Affordable Living in Tacoma', 'With a great location near Interstate 5 and Joint Base Lewis-McChord, The Woodmark provides easily accessible, affordable housing in a convenient south Tacoma neighborhood.', 'Along with access to freeways and multiple bus lines, the community offers authentic home comfort inside its recently renovated one and two bedroom apartments and on-site amenities ideal for both staying active and relaxing.', 'In addition to JBLM, the community places you near city parks, Tacoma Mall, and myriad dining options, including popular spots for Vietnamese and Korean barbecue.', 'To learn more about life at The Woodmark, or the income restrictions associated with this affordable housing community, contact the community today.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 23', 'OR Text', '23', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 750 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Equipped Kitchens', '- Large Closets', '- Full Size Washers & Dryers*', '- Spacious Layouts', '- Balcony or Patio', 'Community Amenities', '- Beautiful Park-Like Setting', '- Ample Parking', '- Two Playgrounds', '- Laundry Facilities', '- Seasonal Swimming Pool', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $300 deposit and a $250 non-refundable fee per pet.', 'Pet rent is $20 per pet per month.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'The Woodmark', '2425 South 96th Street , Tacoma, WA, 98444', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'pOfcxT1H36']
